Q10. We want to find out the most popular music Genre for each country. We determine the most popular genre as the genre with the highest amount of purchases. Write a query that returns each country along with the top Genre. For countries where the maximu
m number of purchases is shared return all Genres.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid14832555 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid6907719\charrsid11144027 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid6907719 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cf20\insrsid6907719\charrsid6907719 SELECT 
\par     country_name,
\par     genre_name,
\par     total_quantity
\par FROM (
\par     SELECT 
\par         c.country AS country_name,
\par         g.name AS genre_name,
\par         SUM(il.Quantity) AS total_quantity,
\par         RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY c.country ORDER BY SUM(il.Quantity) DESC) AS rnk
\par     FROM 
\par         customer c 
\par     JOIN 
\par         invoice i ON c.customer_id = i.customer_id
\par     JOIN 
\par         invoice_line il ON il.invoice_id = i.invoice_id
\par     JOIN 
\par         track t ON il.track_id = t.track_id
\par     JOIN 
\par         genre g ON t.genre_id = g.genre_id
\par     GROUP BY  
\par         1, 2
\par ) AS abc 
\par WHERE rnk = 1;}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cf20\insrsid2434399 
